Aston Villa have made a shock deadline day bid for Real Sociedad playmaker Sergio Canales.

The 23-year-old is a former Real Madrid prospect and would add to Paul Lambert's thin midfield options.

Karim El Ahamadi is heading out of the Villa Park exit door, while Manchester United's Tom Cleverley is stalling on a move.

